1
00:01:20,319 --> 00:01:21,760
Blade God Pork Shop

2
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,040
Blade God Pork Shop

3
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:26,280
Don't miss out, folks, step right up!

4
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,959
Fresh pork here!

5
00:01:27,959 --> 00:01:29,319
Every cut as fresh as can be!

6
00:01:29,879 --> 00:01:30,959
Friends and neighbors,

7
00:01:31,439 --> 00:01:32,519
you have no idea

8
00:01:32,519 --> 00:01:34,439
just how dangerous it was back then.

9
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:35,680
That Chen Hui,

10
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:36,840
my wife knows,

11
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,840
he was a cold-blooded killer.

12
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,319
That's right.

13
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:40,480
But

14
00:01:40,959 --> 00:01:42,760
I ran circles around him.

15
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:43,799
For real?

16
00:01:44,159 --> 00:01:44,799
For real.

17
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,760
I'm telling you, you'd better believe it.

18
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:50,159
My wife was the one who saved me.

19
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,159
Don't believe me? Ask her.

20
00:01:51,159 --> 00:01:51,799
Really?

21
00:01:51,799 --> 00:01:52,439
It's true.

22
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:53,719
And speaking of the explosion,

23
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,319
that was something else entirely.

24
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:56,439
Look behind you.

25
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:57,680
See that building?

26
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,439
Right there, right there.

27
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:01,439
Half of it got blown to pieces.

28
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,239
And me,

29
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,719
well, because

30
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:05,959
I helped the police crack the case,

31
00:02:05,959 --> 00:02:07,319
I got commended for it.

32
00:02:07,319 --> 00:02:08,639
The government even awarded me

33
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:09,800
a Good Samaritan certificate.

34
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,960
And cash too. It's at home.

35
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:12,919
You're joking.

36
00:02:13,159 --> 00:02:14,080
So, which cut?

37
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:14,879
Two jin of pork belly.

38
00:02:14,879 --> 00:02:15,319
This piece.

39
00:02:15,719 --> 00:02:16,360
Would you like some, miss?

40
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:18,199
Sure, I'll weigh it for you in a sec.

41
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:19,159
I'll take this one.

42
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:21,560
Got plenty, all you want.

43
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,159
I'll take this.

44
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,120
Blade God Pork Shop!

45
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,439
Every cut as fresh as can be!

46
00:02:36,439 --> 00:02:37,960
Auntie's here again, here again!

47
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,199
How many months along?

48
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,800
Six more months.

49
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,560
Almost due.

50
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,439
You see, we

51
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:44,719
plan to answer the national call,

52
00:02:44,719 --> 00:02:46,879
have three kids within two years.

53
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:48,120
How can you have that many?

54
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:49,560
Which cut do you want?

55
00:03:11,479 --> 00:03:12,000
Qibao.

56
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,400
Turns out the hardest part

57
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:21,520
isn't being unable to see you,

58
00:03:22,039 --> 00:03:23,599
it's that in every corner of daily life,

59
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,599
you're everywhere.

60
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,039
Chu Feng.

61
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,400
Hurry up.

62
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,879
Make it quick.

63
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:07,439
Kill me.

64
00:04:08,039 --> 00:04:09,599
Make it quick.

65
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:15,280
Chen Hui confessed to all his crimes.

66
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:18,040
Soon after the death penalty verdict,

67
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:18,959
Chen Hui,

68
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,720
refusing all medical treatment,

69
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,160
died in agony.

70
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:29,639
Mentor.

71
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,279
I caught Chen Dahui.

72
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:37,120
He got the punishment he deserved.

73
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,600
It's just that, so often,

74
00:04:42,399 --> 00:04:44,279
I wish we could play chess one more time.

75
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,839
I'll keep moving forward.

76
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:57,319
I'll be right beside you.

77
00:05:10,759 --> 00:05:11,879
We'll fight together.

78
00:05:12,519 --> 00:05:14,360
Not for a bullet of revenge,

79
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,360
but for an answer,

80
00:05:17,319 --> 00:05:19,240
the truth of this fickle world.

81
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,120
Loss

82
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,199
weighs life down.

83
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:26,360
We can only carry our scars and pain,

84
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:27,920
and press on under the weight.

85
00:05:43,319 --> 00:05:43,920
Actually,

86
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,240
the chess game my father left unfinished

87
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,519
wasn't some deeply mysterious puzzle.

88
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,120
Once you figure it out,

89
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:52,279
everything falls into place.

90
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,000
My mentor always used to tell me,

91
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:59,079
"The weak see only obstacles;

92
00:05:59,399 --> 00:06:01,120
the strong see only paths."

93
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,560
Dad,

94
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:05,920
the case is closed.

95
00:06:06,319 --> 00:06:07,399
No matter how tough a case is,

96
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:08,879
as long as you persevere,

97
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,079
it can be solved.

98
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,040
Chu Feng,

99
00:06:18,639 --> 00:06:19,319
it's your birthday.

100
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:20,439
I didn't buy you a gift,

101
00:06:20,439 --> 00:06:21,480
and I haven't had time to.

102
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,279
This watch

103
00:06:22,279 --> 00:06:23,240
has been with me for many years.

104
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,079
It's yours now.

105
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:25,519
No, no.

106
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:26,160
Mentor, I can't accept this.

107
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:26,839
Take it.

108
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:27,639
Take it.

109
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:33,800
Thank you, mentor.

110
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,959
No need to be so polite with me.

111
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:35,360
Thank you.

112
00:06:40,879 --> 00:06:41,360
Hello?

113
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,240
Okay, understood.

114
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,360
We're on our way.

115
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:45,959
We've got a mission.

116
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:48,199
Chu Feng,

117
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,079
come back soon.

118
00:06:50,439 --> 00:06:51,240
There's something I want to tell you.

119
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,360
The other day you said

120
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,560
you had something to say when we got back.

121
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:06,680
What was it you wanted to say?

122
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:06,240
I'm Chu Feng,

123
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,759
an ordinary Police Officer.

124
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:11,240
The demons we hunt down

125
00:09:11,639 --> 00:09:13,639
will be forgotten in dark corners.

126
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,600
The applause we earn

127
00:09:16,639 --> 00:09:18,480
will eventually fade into silence.

128
00:09:19,799 --> 00:09:20,480
Every time I head out,

129
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,240
I still remember my mentor's words.

130
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,080
We wear this uniform

131
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:28,120
not for the title of "hero."

132
00:09:29,279 --> 00:09:30,759
We pull all-nighters and fight on

133
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,000
so that no matter how late it is,

134
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:34,600
the people

135
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:37,519
can walk through this city without fear.

136
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:51,639
Get that changed for me.

137
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:53,399
I like marble, you know that?

138
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,519
What the heck is this?

139
00:09:55,519 --> 00:09:56,720
Looks like a waterfall cave.

140
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:58,080
What are you, a bunch of monkeys?

141
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,879
Don't bother installing that one.

142
00:10:00,879 --> 00:10:01,759
Get rid of it.

143
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,519
Hello.

144
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:13,759
Qibao.

145
00:10:14,759 --> 00:10:15,200
No,

146
00:10:15,759 --> 00:10:16,559
Qibao who?

147
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,759
My surname is Li.

148
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,320
I'm Li Damei.
